      <div class="msgContentFrame">There is no reason to use Avast! I had been an Avast/AVG user for many years, switching depending on performance and ability to catch stuff, mainly because I like a free AV. <br /> <br />Switch to Microsoft's security essentials, it's free, does not impact your system at all (as in does not affect gaming), and the scanner is way better than Avast! or AVG. Did I mention it's free? <br /> <br /><a href="http://www.microsoft.com/security_essentials" title="http://www.microsoft.com/security_essentials" rel="external nofollow">http://www.microsoft.com/security_essentials</a></div>
